["note","E5-S1-T3",1774231746,"c69e037b-ef1d-4875-a05f-f5f0bd436682",{"msg":"Expanded scope per L16: fix has two parts. (1) ComputeReady should surface tasks whose parent is open (not just in-progress) — removes the bootstrap deadlock where a fresh session sees an empty ready queue even though unclaimed tasks exist. (2) When a task is claimed, auto-transition any open ancestor story/epic to in-progress. Current DoD only covers part (2). Update scope to also include internal/ready/compute.go parent-status gate fix."}]
["transition","E5-S0-T1",1774232136,"c69e037b-ef1d-4875-a05f-f5f0bd436682",{"to":"done","outcome":"Added confidence field to op Payload and materialized Issue; draft gate in ComputeReady excludes draft nodes; existing nodes without confidence default to verified; --confidence flag on trls create; 9 new tests (unit + integration); make check green"}]
